se xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 28, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fhw1665702617359.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fhw1665702617359.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fhw1665702617359.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fhw1665702617359\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the type of border for editable Unifields.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__topic_d147005e1_d147006e1_d147007e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__p_d147008e1_d147009e1_d147010e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TextFrame</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">None</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Plain</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Etched</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Bevelled</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Shaded</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__section_w16ab1b5b3_w17ab1b5_w18ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__table_d18026e1_d18027e1_d18028e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Etched</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzj1665702614359.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzj1665702614359.html\" title=\"The [upi] section of the initialization file determines the appearance or behavior of many Universal Presentation Interface (UPI) objects under Microsoft Windows.\">[upi]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__section_gmd_2nh_zvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d545569e118\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__ul_pdt_2nh_zvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__li_d51086e1_d51087e1_d51088e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">None</code>—no border </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__li_d51089e1_d51090e1_d51091e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Plain</code>—narrow black line </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__li_d51092e1_d51093e1_d51094e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Etched</code>—makes the field appear\n               sunken </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__li_d51095e1_d51096e1_d51097e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Bevelled</code>—makes the field appear\n               raised </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__li_d51098e1_d51099e1_d51100e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Shaded</code>—more native shading\n               effect </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fhw1665702617359__section_ap1_fnh_zvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d545569e152\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Editable Unifields fields can optionally have a border, which can make components more\n            attractive.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Etched</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">Bevelled</code> work best when the background of\n            the component is not white or dark gray, because these are the colors used to draw the\n            frame. On a white background, <code class=\"ph codeph\">Shaded</code> looks quite attractive.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Unifieds that are not editable do not have a border.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527509\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527509\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "TextFrame Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 28, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the type of border for editable Unifields. TextFrame = None | Plain | Etched | Bevelled | Shaded Default value Etched File section [upi] Arguments None —no border Plain —narrow black line Etched —makes the field appear sunken Bevelled —makes the field appear raised Shaded —more native shading effect Description Editable Unifields fields can optionally have a border, which can make components more attractive. Etched and Bevelled work best when the background of the component is not white or dark gray, because these are the colors used to draw the frame. On a white background, Shaded looks quite attractive. Unifieds that are not editable do not have a border. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}